{"tid":1636112,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"(緊急)主線任務要人！","createTime":"2019-10-07T16:38:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T17:21:48.000Z","uid":47293,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"012bcfcbc2282711c5f09e28eb88d61b7a3f6a1e","tid":1636112,"uid":47293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:38:24.000Z","msg":"由6月至今<br />\n我地主線任務一直係五大訴求<br />\n港共政府，狗隻同建制派係我地首要目標<br />\n但時至今日，任何高官，建制派都冇被問責懲罰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於其他鋪頭同藍絲算係支線黎<br />\n但而家好多風向撚主張無差別裝修<br />\n咁樣好易失焦 比港共轉移視線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">個人認為神獸同裝修要有原則<br />\n好似神獸係人地出手先召喚<br />\n裝修就黑裝修 紅裝飾 藍罷買 </span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望大家唔好中對家分化之計<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">無論休息撚，勇武撚，唱歌撚，咩職業既都係自己人<br />\n不完美，可改善<br />\n<br />\n主線任務 行動post為先<br />\n記住我地係無大台 <br />\n好多時都要不停檢討先會進步<br />\n做法唔完美就提出<br />\n而唔係分化式屈手足做鬼同割蓆</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n不割蓆不篤灰不分化<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"b098fc52d95d150390fead2669c88e301e89be74","tid":1636112,"uid":47293,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:40:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/10/05/214712_bd97859af4047a504cc74f30363b52f7.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F10%2F05%2F214712_bd97859af4047a504cc74f30363b52f7.jpeg&h=3238854b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/71XK9yf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F71XK9yf.jpg&h=5036a91f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/10/05/215234_79bb8e67def8de5d9427652c1037e468.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F10%2F05%2F215234_79bb8e67def8de5d9427652c1037e468.jpeg&h=4a17bab0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SF27nUh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSF27nUh.jpg&h=1e1a6918&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v3AT2UL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv3AT2UL.jpg&h=b4f0196d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f2d39c63c6a39b03cbb7289c311c7f1c5875aef1","tid":1636112,"uid":47293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:40:46.000Z","msg":"不割蓆不分化"},{"pid":"7867e072c3e4f410e94d4f7ce731443160faccf3","tid":1636112,"uid":47293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:41:09.000Z","msg":"和勇合一"},{"pid":"0df6eca74e347d9879e309b1bf6d192b06f5f35c","tid":1636112,"uid":47293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:41:38.000Z","msg":"721 831"},{"pid":"1db8f0cea18b100527e251431e05765d4f161a75","tid":1636112,"uid":47293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:41:57.000Z","msg":"不割蓆不分化"},{"pid":"9b910b18f1b1098ed08e0e7bb449f8c31bfdc12f","tid":1636112,"uid":47293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:42:11.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"a639186dd88b13f20403151d49354304683290e0","tid":1636112,"uid":47293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:42:21.000Z","msg":"時代革命"},{"pid":"5433a08dad615701fd5f2334bde7a02a05f4196a","tid":1636112,"uid":47293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:42:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"755262082b32a450531013422a31a884b74734d4","tid":1636112,"uid":47293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":